==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Glass-rope
<hw>Glass"-rope`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A remarkable vitreous sponge, of the genus <gen>Hyalonema</gen>,
first brought from Japan. It has a long stem, consisting of a bundle of
long and large, glassy, siliceous fibers, twisted together.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glass-snail</ent>⟦br⟧
